操作指南</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/</link><description>Recent content in 操作指南 on Cloudpods</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Nov 2021 14:39:13 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Docs: 负载均衡实例</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/lb/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Dec 2021 16:07:12 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/lb/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Docs: 监听</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/listener/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Dec 2021 17:04:50 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/listener/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Docs: 转发策略</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/forward/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Dec 2021 16:47:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/forward/</guid><description>
&lt;p>仅HTTP和HTTPS类型的监听支持设置转发策略。配置转发策略后将来自不同域名或URL的请求转发给不同的后端服务器组处理。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">
&lt;h4 class="alert-heading">说明&lt;/h4>
当用户发起HTTP/HTTPS请求时，将会优先匹配转发策略上的配置将请求重定向或转发到对应的后端服务器组，如果不能匹配转发策略，则将匹配监听上的配置将请求重定向或转发到对应的后端服务器组。
&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Docs: 后端服务器组</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/backend/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Dec 2021 16:48:13 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/backend/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Docs: 访问控制</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/access/</link><pubDate>Thu, 16 Dec 2021 17:23:49 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/access/</guid><description>
&lt;p>访问控制用于设置访问负载均衡的IP白名单或IP黑名单，在访问控制策略组中仅可以设置IP地址范围，在配置负载均衡实例监听时可设置是否启用访问控制，并设置针对具体的访问控制策略组设置访问白名单或黑名单。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Docs: 证书</title><link>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/cert/</link><pubDate>Fri, 17 Dec 2021 15:53:30 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.cloudpods.org/zh/docs/multicloud/loadbalancer/tutorial/cert/</guid><description>
&lt;p>当在负载均衡实例上配置HTTPS监听转发来自HTTPS协议的请求时，需要配置证书。负载均衡只支持PEM格式的证书。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>